com.microsoft.VSCode  .kt         all
com.microsoft.VSCode  .scala      all
com.microsoft.VSCode  .ex         all
com.microsoft.VSCode  .exs        all

# Web Frameworks - VS Code
com.microsoft.VSCode  .vue        all
com.microsoft.VSCode  .svelte     all
com.microsoft.VSCode  .astro      all

# Infrastructure as Code - VS Code
com.microsoft.VSCode  .tf         all
com.microsoft.VSCode  .tfvars     all
com.microsoft.VSCode  .hcl        all
com.microsoft.VSCode  .nix        all

# API Schemas - VS Code
