# Justfile / Makefile - VS Code
com.microsoft.VSCode  justfile    all
com.microsoft.VSCode  Justfile    all
com.microsoft.VSCode  Makefile    all
com.microsoft.VSCode  makefile    all

# Dotfiles and hidden configs - VS Code
com.microsoft.VSCode  .cursorrules  all
com.microsoft.VSCode  .cursorignore  all
